it was mine to sell.

579
00:42:40,056 --> 00:42:44,160
And then I remembered why
I wrote my first column.

580
00:42:44,193 --> 00:42:48,164
Because I was
scared and alone.

581
00:42:48,197 --> 00:42:50,967
