alone anymore.

582
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:54,504
I look forward to collaborating
with Modern Media Works

583
00:42:54,537 --> 00:42:57,039
and their talented
marketing team.

584
00:42:57,073 --> 00:43:00,042
