nobody saw him?

716
00:53:39,715 --> 00:53:42,918
- We showed his picture to
every single person. No luck.

717
00:53:42,951 --> 00:53:45,154
Hopefully, the
surveillance cameras

718
00:53:45,187 --> 00:53:46,655
